#: ../docs/source/setup/ssh_proxycommand.rst:7
msgid ""
"This page explains how to use the ``proxy_command`` feature of ``ssh``. This"
" feature is needed when you want to connect to a computer ``B``, but you are"
" not allowed to connect directly to it; instead, you have to connect to "
"computer ``A`` first, and then perform a further connection from ``A`` to "
"``B``."
msgstr ""
"该页面描述了如何使用 ``ssh`` 的 ``proxy_command`` 功能。当你需要连接主机 ``B`` ，但你又不能直接连接该主机； "
"你不得不先连接主机 ``A`` ，再从主机A连接主机B。 这时，你会需要这个功能。"

